    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the magic. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed with love, and driven with the utmost care. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition, looking and feeling just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. Every time I get behind the wheel, it puts a massive smile on my face, and I know it\u2019ll do the same for you. It\u2019s a pristine ride that\u2019s ready for many more miles of memories. Come take a look and see for yourself why I'm so proud of it!",
