      "description": "Presenting a masterfully preserved specimen that truly redefines the 'mint' designation. This unit features a powertrain optimized for peak volumetric efficiency, with recent bore-scope inspections confirming zero cylinder wall scoring and perfect compression symmetry. The high-pressure VANOS system has been recalibrated for instantaneous valve timing response, while the chassis benefits from reinforced subframe mounting points to ensure maximum torsional rigidity. Every suspension bushing has been verified for durometer integrity, paired with a steering rack that offers surgical feedback and zero lash. Finished in a factory-spec depth-calibrated coat with multi-stage ceramic preservation, this vehicle represents a zero-tolerance approach to mechanical excellence. Truly a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast who understands the value of preventative engineering.",
      "price": 48950.0,
